data.description: Price Reduced on this charming listing in highly desirable East Hill nestled in a picturesque setting! This one level classic all Brick home offers a prime opportunity for those seeking a midcentury gem. The home sits gracefully on its spacious lot, showcasing the stately grandeur that East Hill is renowned for. While some restoration is needed, this property presents an exciting canvas for revitalization. Its original features and distinctive character make it a perfect fit for those who appreciate the East Hill classics. The interior boasts spaciousness and original architectural details, while the wonderful backyard offers a tranquil retreat. Located in one of Greshams most sought after neighborhoods, this home offers a perfect blend of convenience and serenity. Enjoy proximity to amenities, parks and schools, all while relishing in the peaceful ambiance. Embrace the chance to restore and transform this gem into a stunning masterpiece that reflects your personal style.
